{"tid":1775293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解大部分人對80萬呢個數字嘅睇法咁單一?","createTime":"2019-12-08T18:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T12:42:43.000Z","uid":77393,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f05e7ea781d576fdb7d8ff767bafa2ddcb915fd2","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:33:34.000Z","msg":"全部人只係解讀成80-200=-120<br />\n散播一種好多人放棄抗爭嘅現象 我哋流失咗120萬位手足<br />\n但點解只有一個咁單一又負面嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無庸置疑 經歷一場長期戰爭 有人會不斷升級抗爭形式 有人會放棄<br />\n<br />\n但其實今日我對80萬遊行人數係咁睇<br />\n<br />\n的確比起我哋6月時引以為傲嘅200萬人遊行係少咗好多人 但唔代表民意逆轉<br />\n大家搞清楚以下幾點 諗嘢要大局觀啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 區議會選舉結果<br />\n<br />\n2星期前嘅區議會有7成投票率 人數超過290萬 坊間一直講民主建制係6:4 咁計法即係有170萬係投民主派 再加上一大班學生 甚至藍絲亦會對政府不滿 基本上人數其實仍然keep到大約200萬甚至更多<br />\n<br />\n簡單講民意歸邊係事實 同時唔存在大量民意流失嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n2. 黑警多次打壓和平集會<br />\n<br />\n由6月到今日12月 足有半年 近期所有集會、遊行都受到黑警無理打壓 濫權濫捕嘅事件更係愈趨嚴重 不論係數字上 手法上都有明顯升級現象<br />\n<br />\n所以和理非的確會因此卻步 即使有不反<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 你知我知 和平集會作用=0<br />\n<br />\n近期基本上大部分連登仔都知和平集會/遊行係冇用 明知政府唔會聽任何訴求 但到今日反而咁着緊遊行人數？？？<br />\n咁我哋實行咗咁多星期嘅黎明行動代表啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n因此 我想帶出嘅係<br />\n<br />\n1. 今日有80萬位手足出嚟係好多人 好高興大家一齊完成呢個創舉<br />\n<br />\n2. 流失嘅120萬人並不代表全部放棄晒 而可以從區選結果引證 呢班大多數只係因為近月被政府漠視民意+黑警無理打壓 而選擇唔參與遊行活動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">係代表有120萬人對政府黑警嘅不信任 決定杯葛和平表達訴求嘅示威活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n足足有120萬人唔相信政府所提倡嘅和平示威 係落咗林鄭面 係以杯葛形式表達對政權嘅不滿<br />\n呢個數字對一個聲稱注重民意嘅政府係極不理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一句 希望大家唔好受失敗主義影響 今日人數有80萬係好值得自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然 我哋亦需要開始為抗爭轉型亦係不爭嘅事實 由今日起遊行呢個活動形式或者要暫時告一段落 建議應該加重經濟攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4dd2980e6e500bcc97c5ba24a57deda73c21c0de","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:34:08.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"7a013e69263c8243d5265902daa47310a2ef52af","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:34:20.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"402144115b078ac6b5ff792649c8082f8d006668","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:34:32.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"e30a9501080dbdf8a61ca8baa0b1bd55b6f23d1f","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:34:47.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"73a0741af3bc86036e97ad27fb64b947af587a54","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:35:02.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"2a9bf25a0afea9ddf64952c68d9fb5a85431161a","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:35:18.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"35ff5d3e7bbfb75e2fa73982a69ae87c93ddfaa8","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:35:39.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"f916b8b1a09fa0281948ed9a1c0bd9997a3897c3","tid":1775293,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:35:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ba25729aed666f4119e3978574de6e49bcb35a8","tid":1775293,"uid":223678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7387e20986afc9941c67a4f584bade8c9266b8a7","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:36:01.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"d989656272078ea187d9ffc4059472d3866ed0ce","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:36:44.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"90e5a14c0a63ed8203ada926a8bcfa8822219c51","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:37:05.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"26237198670a86b205e0d6cef1bd17486a9e7e68","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:37:21.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"fbc38dbf1f3ac7ec670fdf03f3602c63673f70cb","tid":1775293,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T19:33:48.000Z","msg":"從來數據都係由人去演繹，呢方面真係要學下啲狗，好耐之前有個po 整合左啲狗有幾咁厚面皮，點樣擘大眼講大話。如果連呢點做唔好唔好話同林鄭對抗，連狗都可以無恥死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1dba5ff6611a94f0bcdcbc06e291c81c964590","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:29:01.000Z","msg":"瞓醒再推 11/20"},{"pid":"ed14adf62327197947b7750694092912822053ce","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:29:12.000Z","msg":"12/20"},{"pid":"0c195611ee4381bc0bf3e82813c7d3845b80d958","tid":1775293,"uid":77393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbc38dbf1f3ac7ec670fdf03f3602c63673f70cb","tid":1775293,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T19:33:48.000Z","msg":"從來數據都係由人去演繹，呢方面真係要學下啲狗，好耐之前有個po 整合左啲狗有幾咁厚面皮，點樣擘大眼講大話。如果連呢點做唔好唔好話同林鄭對抗，連狗都可以無恥死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:31:27.000Z","msg":"其實政治真係要識'玩' 但香港人太善良 話就話明體制內抗爭冇效 但就一直好守規矩"},{"pid":"86dc0a8be8e7e1917cae570c3598518f7edffe93","tid":1775293,"uid":81560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9908ca9be09f435335f2fba761d09a9caae761c8","tid":1775293,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tfor3kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftfor3kb.jpg&h=3bdf14ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMKVWE8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMKVWE8.jpg&h=ef7e3361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSvh9Z7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSvh9Z7.jpg&h=1e87f419&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c03a436da38d74df9d26e7432c1f1629c8e14830","tid":1775293,"uid":274996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"因為真。香港人對自己要求高，呢樣有好有唔好。同時佢地都知道香港人一直以來既惡習：3分鐘熱度，善忘，容易對權威妥協，搵錢行先。<br />\n<br />\n佢地擔心個數字，其實係怕香港人又返到半年前對社會不聞不問既心態。唯有希望香港人能堅持下去，就算冇衝突場面，政府警察唔再自爆，都唔好忘記爭取民主自由既心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZsAenF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZsAenF.jpg&h=d4e00427&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad8fdf9ba937890c352024155199e01a8d91957f","tid":1775293,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:42:05.000Z","msg":"6月遊行，好多朋友拖男帶女來<br />\n依家會避免小朋友出來，夫婦二人又要留一人睇細路<br />\n<br />\n唔講上晝POPO又出新聞嚇人"},{"pid":"27a28255400d9f1dcf9f52758e675a874d3dbe78","tid":1775293,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:43:30.000Z","msg":"民陣次次報細數<br />\n做維穩<br />\n大家要同民陣割"},{"pid":"af7db500d08bbf0a3981eaad5e3a8f5fc88e7d5b","tid":1775293,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:17:34.000Z","msg":"6月講過<br />\n200萬人果日你要鳩行<br />\n就一定呢世都眾唔返200萬人<br />\n<br />\n另一方面<br />\n200萬人鳩行無用<br />\n唔通少過200萬會有用？<br />\n<br />\n呢啲嘢大家心知肚明<br />\n亦因為明白所先先唔再出嚟<br />\n<br />\n何必再格硬搵啲嘢做去呃自己運動持續緊呢"},{"pid":"2d92f505be93aa3bc3846618e185529ada874329","tid":1775293,"uid":171058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:50:21.000Z","msg":"尋日我覺得係過100，真心唔明點解話得80<br />\n因為冇入維園所以唔count?<br />\n超多人唔係唔想入維園，係根本入唔到去<br />\n灣仔行過去，去到鵝頸橋已經塞死行唔到<br />\n有人天后果邊入，企咗8個字都冇郁過<br />\n最後睇住D人掉頭，由灣仔變成隊頭開始行"}]}